Dialogue: 9,0:00:01.31,0:00:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And so,
Dialogue: 9,0:00:03.06,0:00:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}in the Roman Republic, the landholding aristocracy held the major government offices,
Dialogue: 9,0:00:08.23,0:00:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}creating a clear class division between the Patricians, or aristocrats, and the Plebians, or commoners and farmers.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:15.06,0:00:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is boring.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:18.84,0:00:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The two consuls or the dictator and 300 \Nsenators were chosen from the aristocracy.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:27.04,0:00:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The Senate was the highest legislative and advisory body.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:30.81,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A senator's term of office was—
Dialogue: 9,0:00:34.43,0:00:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that coming from 1-A?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:36.23,0:00:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Omichi-sensei?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:37.40,0:00:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:44.06,0:00:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's definitely 1-A.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:46.01,0:00:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on there?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:47.01,0:00:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? I'll bet Omichi's lost it again.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:03.67,0:01:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Chitanda?
Dialogue: 9,0:01:14.89,0:01:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, alright, let's carry on then.
Dialogue: 9,0:01:19.24,0:01:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where was I again?
Dialogue: 9,0:01:21.93,0:01:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I at the Senate?
