Dialogue: 9,0:03:00.28,0:03:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who said you were going to do it!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down, Mayaka-san...
Dialogue: 9,0:03:08.51,0:03:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, Chii-chan.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:10.41,0:03:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you have a reason, but that's besides the point!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:12.40,0:03:13.99,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, Mayaka-san!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:13.31,0:03:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could have at least called me or something!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.70,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some cookies?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:16.09,0:03:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}This could have been avoided if you had just contacted me!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:19.02,0:03:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you had your cell phone with you! {timing check}
Dialogue: 9,0:03:19.98,0:03:22.49,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! How about I go get some milk?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:20.67,0:03:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be fine if it were just a hassle for me, but it's not!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:25.23,0:03:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:26.66,0:03:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand your position here?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:27.61,0:03:30.88,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda Eru doesn't know when to quit.{無謀な人間 (she's reckless to try and get inbetween Ibara and her prey)}
Dialogue: 9,0:03:28.61,0:03:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This won't be fixed just by saying sorry to me.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:31.38,0:03:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I know you're aware of it,
Dialogue: 9,0:03:33.40,0:03:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't have a shred of decency when it matters.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:33.59,0:03:34.87,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even bother.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:36.50,0:03:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't say anything, even though you knew what would happen.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:39.15,0:03:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, it rained, it was windy, there was lightning, and even hail fell in the end!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:43.64,0:03:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent time picking what to wear, and all of a sudden they're a wreck!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:51.62,0:03:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's all your fault!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:53.20,0:03:54.04,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you tired yet?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then take a break.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't out to help you!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:06.89,0:04:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure can get mad.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:10.26,0:04:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet you let out a lot of stress there.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:12.41,0:04:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had more common decency, I \Nwouldn't get stressed in the first place.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:16.47,0:04:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should take a lesson from Chitanda-san.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:20.76,0:04:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never even seen her get angry.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:23.59,0:04:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're going to say that, I've never seen you or Oreki-san get angry, either...
Dialogue: 9,0:04:31.94,0:04:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuku-chan totally gets angry.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really does.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:37.85,0:04:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:41.10,0:04:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't display it as obviously as Mayaka, but I do every now and then.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:45.04,0:04:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I find that hard to imagine...
Dialogue: 9,0:04:48.67,0:04:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am only human. Of course I get angry.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:52.14,0:04:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't show your emotions in front of others.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:57.05,0:04:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's nothing special when you get angry.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing special?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:01.22,0:05:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do look down on me...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:03.57,0:05:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually a bit curious now...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:06.95,0:05:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can imagine Chitanda planning something to get him riled up.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That could be fun.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:14.78,0:05:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get angry, Oreki-san?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:18.15,0:05:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he'd get angry.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:20.39,0:05:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's easy going?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:22.10,0:05:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, because he's a sad excuse of a human who can't even get angry.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:26.87,0:05:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's just mean!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:30.31,0:05:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey look, I got angry!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:32.50,0:05:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Houtarou's lack of emotions aside,
Dialogue: 9,0:05:35.20,0:05:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Chitanda never getting angry is a special case.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:38.98,0:05:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should try to emulate some of that calmness of hers.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:45.09,0:05:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I can change that part of me just by trying.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be like Chii-chan.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:50.74,0:05:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... that doesn't sound like a compliment...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:53.83,0:05:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it might be, actually.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just making observations.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not inherently good or bad.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:59.15,0:06:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who are unable to get angry are a different story,
Dialogue: 9,0:06:02.16,0:06:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think it's an excellent trait not to get angry.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:04.87,0:06:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrath is a serious sin, after all.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:07.24,0:06:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should scale back on your outbursts, Mayaka.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sin?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:11.01,0:06:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seven deadly sins, right?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. I figured you'd know, Chitanda-san.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've heard of them too, right?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:18.95,0:06:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know of them.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:22.04,0:06:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, aren't there 108 sins?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Buddhism.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:26.34,0:06:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrath, pride, gluttony, greed...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:33.27,0:06:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Envy, lust, and sloth, right?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:35.78,0:06:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:36.99,0:06:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sloth, huh?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at me?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:40.25,0:06:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that makes you perfect, Chii-chan.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're diligent, and you don't overeat.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:45.58,0:06:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine you being greedy, and you're definitely not lazy.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:49.86,0:06:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:50.62,0:06:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're not into... dirty things.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:53.49,0:06:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:54.47,0:06:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to tell if she's envious of anyone, though.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two aren't even complimenting her anymore...
Dialogue: 9,0:06:59.68,0:07:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just teasing her.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:01.42,0:07:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop this!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:02.81,0:07:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, when I get hungry I can eat a lot!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:02.81,0:07:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She doesn't seem the envious type, either.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So would anyone.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:07.39,0:07:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should just call her Saint Eru.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:10.10,0:07:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't "Chitanda Eru" sound kind of angelic?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:13.36,0:07:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uriel, Gabriel, Chitandael?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop it!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:21.92,0:07:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got angry.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:23.15,0:07:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She told us off, too.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:25.69,0:07:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Chii-chan.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:27.75,0:07:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:29.71,0:07:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, now you made her mad.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:33.40,0:07:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were totally playing along, too.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:38.20,0:07:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's good thing to never get angry.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:41.84,0:07:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same for the other deadly sins, right?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:46.58,0:07:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think pride and greed are also important.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:50.05,0:07:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:51.45,0:07:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can never feel pride, then that means you have no self confidence.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:57.40,0:08:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And someone who never feels greed wouldn't be able to support their family.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:03.75,0:08:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New technologies would never have been invented if people never felt envy.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:12.42,0:08:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I didn't mean to turn this into a lecture...
Dialogue: 9,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Interesting...
Dialogue: 9,0:08:19.60,0:08:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that it's a matter of degree?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:22.55,0:08:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's useful to just take the deadly sins as absolute and apply that to our lives.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:30.56,0:08:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't think it's necessarily bad to get angry?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:34.44,0:08:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:35.81,0:08:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can never get angry at anything, that probably means you have nothing that you like, either.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:40.96,0:08:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do get angry. Yep.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:43.58,0:08:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's the case, why don't you ever get angry?
Dialogue: 9,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it tires me out.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:48.79,0:08:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I like to avoid getting tired.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:01.31,0:09:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitanda-san's been poisoned by Houtarou!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:04.65,0:09:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:05.94,0:09:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a ghost haunting Kamiyama High!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:08.44,0:09:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ghost of energy saving!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Chii-chan!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Chii-chan!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:12.20,0:09:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys sure run their mouths...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:14.80,0:09:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just joking!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:17.65,0:09:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a joke.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:21.63,0:09:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A joke, huh?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:22.88,0:09:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I thought I'd found a soul mate.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:26.03,0:09:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I was just playing around.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:31.07,0:09:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I can get angry. And I do.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:36.02,0:09:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, for example...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:42.11,0:09:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get angry when people waste food.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:44.97,0:09:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each grain of rice is a drop of sweat.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:48.85,0:09:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a farmer's daughter for you.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:52.03,0:09:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me...
Dialogue: 9,0:09:53.77,0:09:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that topic, wasn't it you who got angry in Omichi's class during fifth period?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:02.69,0:10:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I forget?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:07.66,0:10:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping I could ask you about that!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:11.73,0:10:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:13.18,0:10:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:13.95,0:10:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious! I'm curious!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:15.76,0:10:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious! I'm curious! I'm curious!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:25.07,0:10:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll go home now.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:28.81,0:10:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping I could ask you about that!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:38.20,0:10:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. During fifth period in math class, I got angry.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:46.15,0:10:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got angry?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:47.76,0:10:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know what happened to make me angry.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:53.45,0:10:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no need for me to suddenly get angry,
Dialogue: 9,0:10:56.85,0:11:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but something happened to make me angry,
Dialogue: 9,0:11:00.28,0:11:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know what it was that happened.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:06.05,0:11:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:06.81,0:11:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, I'm not sure what...
Dialogue: 9,0:11:13.35,0:11:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either ways, I'm curious!
